name: infiniFi Locked iUSD (8week)
description: infiniFi is a borrow short lend long fractional reserve system that amplifies yields on existing blue chip yield farms. By matching users with low liquidity preference with those with high liquidity preference infiniFi is able to enhance yields on any asset without having to add any leverage to the system. By melding defi transparency with time tested banking principles infiniFi represents the evolution of on chain balance sheet management. Better than banks.
